query:
select l_extendedprice, l_discount
from orders, lineitem
where o_orderkey = l_orderkey
    and o_orderdate >= date '1993-10-01'
    AND o_orderdate < date '1994-01-01'
    and l_returnflag = 'R'

FROM public.o_p1,
public.l_p3
WHERE o_p1.o_orderkey = l_p3.l_orderkey AND (o_p1.o_orderdate >= DATE '1993-10-01' AND o_p1.o_orderdate < DATE '1994-01-01') AND l_p3.l_returnflag = 'R'
